data.name: ReadCsenetTransactionEnvelop
data.value: select top(1) CCA_TRANSACTION_DT, CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TIMES, PROCESSING_STATUS, ERROR_CODE from CKT_CSENET_TRN_ENV where (CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM = @ccaTransSerNum) and (CCA_TRANSACTION_DT = @ccaTransactionDt)

data.name: ReadInterstateCase
data.value: select top(1) TRANS_SERIAL_NBR, TRANSACTION_DATE from CKT_INTERST_CASE with(readuncommitted) where (TRANS_SERIAL_NBR = @transSerialNbr) and (TRANSACTION_DATE = @transactionDate)

data.name: UpdateCsenetTransactionEnvelop
data.value: update CKT_CSENET_TRN_ENV set LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TIMES = @lastUpdatedTimes, PROCESSING_STATUS = @processingStatus, ERROR_CODE = @errorCode where (CCA_TRANSACTION_DT = @ccaTransactionDt) and (CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM = @ccaTransSerNum)
